626
00:45:38,200 --> 00:45:39,110
Yes.

627
00:45:39,640 --> 00:45:42,040
They'll really have a divorce because of her?

628
00:45:42,530 --> 00:45:43,350
Yes.

629
00:45:43,510 --> 00:45:47,170
