636
00:46:31,930 --> 00:46:37,400
but I just exactly have 57,800 won right now.

637
00:46:39,020 --> 00:46:40,260
What can I do?

638
00:46:41,200 --> 00:46:42,020
Pardon?

639
00:46:42,570 --> 00:46:44,320
You don't have to pay me.

640
00:46:44,750 --> 00:46:47,400
Uncle, you have to make money too.

641
00:46:47,420 --> 00:46:49,980
It's not good to hear that
our economy is in a bad state.

642
00:46:52,240 --> 00:46:53,200
But instead,

643
00:46:53,820 --> 00:46:56,040
be sure to stop your parents from having a divorce.

644
00:46:56,570 --> 00:46:57,420
Promise me.

645
00:47:00,770 --> 00:47:02,000
All right.

646
00:47:02,420 --> 00:47:04,150
Thank you so much.

647
00:47:04,150 --> 00:47:05,180
Okay.

648
00:47:33,280 --> 00:47:34,400
Where are you going?

649
00:47:34,970 --> 00:47:37,180
