677
00:48:52,040 --> 00:48:52,950
Yes.

678
00:48:52,950 --> 00:48:54,170
You're 7 years old?

679
00:48:54,170 --> 00:48:54,950
Yes.

680
00:48:55,240 --> 00:48:58,310
But where is Seongbuk-dong?

681
00:50:50,800 --> 00:50:51,680
Why?

682
00:50:52,260 --> 00:50:53,330
Want to eat some dumplings?

683
00:50:53,570 --> 00:50:56,040
Well, not at all.

684
00:50:57,220 --> 00:51:01,380
But which way shall I go to Seongbuk-dong?

685
00:51:02,930 --> 00:51:03,750
Seongbuk-dong?

686
00:51:03,750 --> 00:51:05,040
Where at Seongbuk-dong?

687
00:51:05,220 --> 00:51:07,620
To where Kim Hee Sun lives.

688
00:51:08,350 --> 00:51:09,170
What?

689
00:51:34,000 --> 00:51:37,080
Grandma, which way is Seongbuk-dong?

690
00:51:37,080 --> 00:51:38,550
Seongbuk-dong?

691
00:51:38,550 --> 00:51:40,000
It's over there.

692
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:40,880
