695
00:53:51,640 --> 00:53:52,480
Kid.

696
00:53:55,240 --> 00:53:56,260
Hey, kid.

697
00:54:06,550 --> 00:54:08,110
Unni...

698
00:54:09,840 --> 00:54:11,020
What's wrong?

699
00:54:13,800 --> 00:54:15,420
Unni...

700
00:54:16,510 --> 00:54:20,710
Can you please break up with my Dad?

701
00:54:40,480 --> 00:54:41,400
But,

702
00:54:41,950 --> 00:54:43,850
