707
00:54:55,600 --> 00:54:56,910
What do you mean in actual?

708
00:54:58,330 --> 00:54:59,970
You've cheated with her!

709
00:55:01,660 --> 00:55:02,080
What?

710
00:55:02,080 --> 00:55:03,170
Stop pretending.

711
00:55:03,170 --> 00:55:04,400
Do you think I don't know?

712
00:55:04,420 --> 00:55:06,280
I've seen everything on your phone.

713
00:55:06,280 --> 00:55:07,260
About Kim Hee Sun.

714
00:55:18,840 --> 00:55:20,950
You just looked at the name,
not on the phone number, didn't you?

715
00:55:21,330 --> 00:55:22,020
What?

716
00:55:23,440 --> 00:55:24,800
It's your phone number.

717
00:55:24,820 --> 00:55:26,280
I said it's yours.

718
00:55:26,570 --> 00:55:27,600
You've been doing your best,

719
00:55:27,600 --> 00:55:30,260
